##### Personal #####

IMAPAccount gmail-aaraines
Host imap.gmail.com
Port 993
User aaraines@gmail.com
PassCmd "gpg2 -q --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty -d ~/.authinfo.gpg | awk '/machine aaraines.*993/ {print $(NF-2)}'"
SSLType IMAPS

IMAPStore gmail-aaraines
Account gmail-aaraines

IMAPAccount local-aaraines
Host localhost
Port 143
User aaraines
Pass secret
SSLType None

IMAPStore local-aaraines
Account local-aaraines

Channel aaraines
Master :gmail-aaraines:
Slave :local-aaraines:
Patterns !* INBOX list.*
MaxSize 100k
MaxMessages 1000
Create Both
Expunge Both
Sync All


